      <title>Sometimes all you need is someone to tell you that you can 🙌🏻 I try to be that v...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/CeOFP4LvUk1/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CeOFP4LvUk1/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/500464018_1223781726005771_9016329210139781255_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mjg1MDIzODY5NTUyMzMwNTc4MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHgxMjgwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=8tNrTOZNyVcQ7kNvwHY1ffS&amp;_nc_oc=AdoaqJIp0y-KbBUe41bHtZEvNV8wIjam31ru2Ye-qUNEQmCkQu6QwJ-KGrl3DaZ3L3s&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=S76YhIzFrLRUQfDT-9Lopg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwATlDw2giadPkklfS2gu4Wpeds-7zLZr4pEUHWjBzKeA&amp;oe=69C9FFDB" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @emmanoa________" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@emmanoa________</strong></p><p>Sometimes all you need is someone to tell you that you can 🙌🏻<br/>
<br/>
I try to be that voice of encouragement for others, but sometimes forget that I need to hear it too. Leo is one of those voices for me. A few days ago I told him that I was far from getting these transitions. He gently told me he didn’t think I was and asked me to try. I got it first attempt. <br/>
<br/>
So so much of the yoga practice is learning when to listen to or ignore that little voice in your mind. Self-belief is so important, and someone reminding you what you are capable of is part of the magic of practicing yoga and finding the teacher who resonates with you. <br/>
<br/>
Thanks for your support and encouraging voice always and always @leo_oppenheim And thanks for co-creating at @skyhutretreats this past week. I am so grateful for it all. <br/>
<br/>
If you get a chance and are interested to practice with him he teaches in-person and online classes and upcoming retreats in- and outside of the UK, and I am exited to co-create more together in the future.</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQOU3A2mfa55VzmB3FDY7WaqDtUHU9sID_Kq2Z-1b_ynlPgPNxgNYlgo-9VlTRBBg0N7R1tRAFqxsuLsY2oODslQeoQ-JjB5IdoBzeg.mp4?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=wWKgZjqTak8Q7kNvwFNMU1U&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6NTQ4NzA0ODIzNTEzNDY4LCJhc3NldF9hZ2VfZGF5cyI6MTM5NCwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjI5LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=6df911d41de16a9b&amp;_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC81OTRFQjlDMEQ2QzE2MTU0MjY1NzZDQTExNDQ1QkU5Ql92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYOnBhc3N0aHJvdWdoX2V2ZXJzdG9yZS9HQ0ZYN3hERkJKWTdMclVGQU9CZXp1dlFmVElLYnFfRUFBQUYVAgLIARIAKAAYABsCiAd1c2Vfb2lsATEScHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmVfcmVjaXBlATEVAAAm-MW8wenC-QEVAigCQzMsF0A9EOVgQYk3GBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX-B2XmnQEA&amp;_nc_gid=S76YhIzFrLRUQfDT-9Lopg&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwLtFhZ8au6sX30oI2ZS8YVCmuGGiD373UTsvNGeZnL5w&amp;oe=69C63CBB">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CeOFP4LvUk1/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CeOFP4LvUk1/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/500464018_1223781726005771_9016329210139781255_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mjg1MDIzODY5NTUyMzMwNTc4MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHgxMjgwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=8tNrTOZNyVcQ7kNvwHY1ffS&amp;_nc_oc=AdoaqJIp0y-KbBUe41bHtZEvNV8wIjam31ru2Ye-qUNEQmCkQu6QwJ-KGrl3DaZ3L3s&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=S76YhIzFrLRUQfDT-9Lopg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwATlDw2giadPkklfS2gu4Wpeds-7zLZr4pEUHWjBzKeA&amp;oe=69C9FFDB" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @emmanoa________" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@emmanoa________</strong></p><p>Sometimes all you need is someone to tell you that you can 🙌🏻<br/>
<br/>
I try to be that voice of encouragement for others, but sometimes forget that I need to hear it too. Leo is one of those voices for me. A few days ago I told him that I was far from getting these transitions. He gently told me he didn’t think I was and asked me to try. I got it first attempt. <br/>
<br/>
So so much of the yoga practice is learning when to listen to or ignore that little voice in your mind. Self-belief is so important, and someone reminding you what you are capable of is part of the magic of practicing yoga and finding the teacher who resonates with you. <br/>
<br/>
Thanks for your support and encouraging voice always and always @leo_oppenheim And thanks for co-creating at @skyhutretreats this past week. I am so grateful for it all. <br/>
<br/>
If you get a chance and are interested to practice with him he teaches in-person and online classes and upcoming retreats in- and outside of the UK, and I am exited to co-create more together in the future.</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQOU3A2mfa55VzmB3FDY7WaqDtUHU9sID_Kq2Z-1b_ynlPgPNxgNYlgo-9VlTRBBg0N7R1tRAFqxsuLsY2oODslQeoQ-JjB5IdoBzeg.mp4?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=wWKgZjqTak8Q7kNvwFNMU1U&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6NTQ4NzA0ODIzNTEzNDY4LCJhc3NldF9hZ2VfZGF5cyI6MTM5NCwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjI5LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=6df911d41de16a9b&amp;_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC81OTRFQjlDMEQ2QzE2MTU0MjY1NzZDQTExNDQ1QkU5Ql92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYOnBhc3N0aHJvdWdoX2V2ZXJzdG9yZS9HQ0ZYN3hERkJKWTdMclVGQU9CZXp1dlFmVElLYnFfRUFBQUYVAgLIARIAKAAYABsCiAd1c2Vfb2lsATEScHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmVfcmVjaXBlATEVAAAm-MW8wenC-QEVAigCQzMsF0A9EOVgQYk3GBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX-B2XmnQEA&amp;_nc_gid=S76YhIzFrLRUQfDT-9Lopg&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwLtFhZ8au6sX30oI2ZS8YVCmuGGiD373UTsvNGeZnL5w&amp;oe=69C63CBB">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CeOFP4LvUk1/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
